## Network Configuration

The following tasks were completed during the network configuration:

- Configured a VirtualBox NAT Network.
- Connected all three virtual machines to the NAT Network.
- Verified that each virtual machine received an IP address through DHCP.
- Confirmed internet connectivity using the host's mobile hotspot.
- Performed connectivity testing between the virtual machines.

