## Challenges

No networking configuration issues were encountered during the setup process. All virtual machines obtained IP addresses successfully through DHCP and internet connectivity was verified. The only observation was that Windows 10 did not respond to ICMP echo requests from Ubuntu Server and Kali Linux, which is most likely due to Windows Firewall settings.

